h1. base

h2. Purpose

Sets a base URL that the other properties can override.

h2. Examples

{code}
UriBuilder.build {
    base = "http://example.com"
}
{code}

h2. Description

Sets a base URL that the other properties can override. Any other properties set in the @UriBuilder@ will override the appropriate parts of the base URL. The only exception to this is the @path@ property,
which will add to the URL path.
